{"word":"Iconium","slug":"iconium","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Iconium</b> A city of Asia Minor.<br/> Paul preaches in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=13&verse=51'>Act 13:51</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=14&verse=22'>Act 14:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=16&verse=2'>Act 16:2</a><br/> Paul is persecuted by the people of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=14&verse=6'>Act 14:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=55&chapter=3&verse=11'>2Ti 3:11</a>"}]}